.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, lavender, yellow, blue, brown
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person who likes blue is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Color   | blue       | brown       | chestnut   | yellow      | lavender    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

