5 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, pony, rat
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, ship, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the police-officer##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the dressmaker and the egyptian##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the firefighter is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the turkish##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the owner of the dog is the mechanic##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Job         | mechanic   | police-officer | firefighter  | engineer | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish     | egyptian   | french     | mexican      |
| Pet           | dog       | pony        | ferret     | horse      | rat          |
| Transport     | ship      | taxi        | helicopter | skateboard | roller       |

